<p><img src="./images/HighLevel.png" alt="HighLevel.png" /></p>

<h2 id="components"><strong>Components</strong></h2>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Recipe</strong> : This is a SAP Cloud Platform cockpit based module acting as user experience layer for recipe. This consists of different reusable utilities for recipe implementors.</li>
  <li><strong>Recipe Service</strong> : This is a Cloud Foundry backend service supporting the backend operations for recipe. This is still <strong>not productive</strong>.</li>
  <li><strong>SLM</strong> : This is the SAP Cloud Platform market place service which stores the recipe contents.</li>
  <li><strong>Authoring Tool</strong> : Tool for recipe authors to document the recipe</li>
</ul>

